{"3264480": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "終焉之森2", "steam_appid": 3264480, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【⚠警告】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>※閱覽注意，本遊戲適合喜歡獵奇、Ryona的玩家。</strong><br><strong>※本遊戲將會出現大量極其血腥暴力的內容。 </strong><br><strong>女主角會反覆經歷死亡，並且死亡場面會直接透過插圖表現出來。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【故事內容】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264480/extras/b2da65dca39aa780d9aa4d4cf9130666.avif?t=1762826128\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在柯爾特進入森林的數年後，原本孱弱的菲露姆在痊癒之後也成為了一名冒險者。<br>在某次下榻的酒館裡，菲露姆耳聞了柯爾特最後前往的方向是「司拉弗之森」。<br>為了追尋姐姐的下落，她也朝森林的方向前去——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但在那前方迎接她的會是多年未見的姐姐，抑或是更多的<strong>絕望</strong>……？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【遊戲特色】</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >硬核虐殺・獵奇視覺小說遊戲 多種死亡劇情</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264480/extras/b70de330a30005c09875aeb8ff1b63c3.avif?t=1762826128\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——被鱷魚型吞噬獸食獣咬下手腳後，肩膀以上的部位也被咬斷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264480/extras/882b0dbc5ef6e3cd6a983f819f574329.avif?t=1762826128\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——被尖銳的岩石刺穿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——承受石化吐息後石化、碎裂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女主角擁有完整日文配音。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【角色介紹】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=